      • verifyAndUpdateAuthority

        public void verifyAndUpdateAuthority(rst.domotic.action.ActionAuthorityType.ActionAuthority actionAuthority,
                                     rst.domotic.authentication.TicketAuthenticatorWrapperType.TicketAuthenticatorWrapper.Builder ticketAuthenticatorWrapperBuilder)
                              throws org.openbase.jul.exception.VerificationFailedException,
                                     org.openbase.jul.exception.PermissionDeniedException,
                                     InterruptedException,
                                     org.openbase.jul.exception.CouldNotPerformException
        Verifies the authority by verifying its internal TicketAuthenticationWrapper with the authenticator and updates the given ticketAuthenticatorWrapperBuilder. It the authenticator has no TicketAuthenticationWrapper, the given ticketAuthenticatorWrapperBuilder is just not updated.
        Parameters:
        actionAuthority - the authority verified
        ticketAuthenticatorWrapperBuilder - the ticketAuthenticator to update.
        Throws:
        org.openbase.jul.exception.VerificationFailedException - if someone is logged in but the verification with the authenticator fails
        org.openbase.jul.exception.PermissionDeniedException - is thrown in case the authority has no permission for the related action.
        InterruptedException
        org.openbase.jul.exception.CouldNotPerformException
